<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.5">
<l>vantikkum maṟṟavarkkum mācuṭampiṉ vallamaṇar tamakku mallēṉ</l>
<l>munticceṉ ṟariyuruvā yiraṇiyaṉai muraṇaḻitta mutalvark kallāl</l>
<l>cantappū malarccōlait taṇcēṟai yemperumāṉ tāḷai nāḷum</l>
<l>cintippārk keṉṉuḷḷam tēṉūṟi yeppoḻutun tittik kummē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am not for those others who “Vandē” or for the hardy ascetics</l>
<l rend="indent">with filthy bodies,</l>
<l>But for the primal one who destroyed Hiraṇya in battle,</l>
<l rend="indent">arriving in front [of him] in a lion form;</l>
<l>My heart, [as if] oozing honey, is always sweet for those who daily meditate</l>
<l>On the feet of our great lord of cool Cēṟai, with groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where sandalwood flowers bloom.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
